    AssociationModel
    A class defining the database model associated to associations.
    CharacterModel
    A DBModel defining the data obtained from a character saved in database.

    A class encapsulating all the data representiong a pseudo given to a character by another one.

    A DBModel defining the data obtained from a event saved in database.

    PlaceModel
    A DBModel defining the data obtained from a place saved in database.
    RelationData
    A class defining the data obtained from a relation saved in database.
